@ mentaljojo - to upload a torrent onto this website:
1. Create a torrent (for example: using utorrent, click "File" then "Create New Torrent" and follow the simple steps)
2. scroll to the bottom of this page and find the "Upload torrent" link on the top row of links. 
3. Select the torrent you want to upload, name it, and then fill in the rest of the details as desired.
4. type the words in the box to prove your humanity
5. click the "Add to index" button below the words you just typed.  Done!
